WEBVTT

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:33.696
Those men

00:00:33.720 --> 00:00:37.856
wanted to create a peaceful,

00:00:37.880 --> 00:00:40.096
democratic Europe,

00:00:40.120 --> 00:00:42.280
a Europe that works for its people.

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:46.576
And one of the many building blocks

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:48.856
in that peace project

00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:50.920
was a common European market.

00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:55.216
Already back then,

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:57.056
they saw how markets,

00:00:57.080 --> 00:00:59.416
when left to themselves,

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:04.495
can sort of slip into being
just the private property